# Seed Lawnchair as the default HOME role holder.
#
# Android 13 has no clean static-overlay path for the HOME role default holder
# (no config_defaultRoleHolders entry in this tree; the role is resolved by
# PermissionController from roles.xml). So we seed it the same way that worked at
# runtime: `cmd package set-home-activity`. The chosen role is stored in /data, so
# this is effectively a one-time seed — re-running on later boots is harmless and
# idempotent. It runs after sys.boot_completed=1 so PackageManager and RoleManager
# are fully up and Lawnchair (installed in /product) has been scanned.
#
# Launcher3QuickStep stays installed as the recents/overview provider
# (config_recentsComponentName); this only changes which activity holds HOME.

on property:sys.boot_completed=1
    exec_background - root root -- /system/bin/cmd package set-home-activity app.lawnchair/app.lawnchair.LawnchairLauncher
